Discovered the essential skills needed to survive in the professional realm by Ts. Hj. Abdul Alim Bin Abdul Muttalib. He also emphasized that while university education laid down the fundamental knowledge, essential practical skills are also very important.
For improvement, I will adopt a more applied learning approach. For each core subject, I will undertake a small personal project that implements the concepts learned. I also will adopt a study group where we review and reapply the knowledge learnt.
